---

## 🚀 How to Run
1. Open `SFO_Class_Divided.sln` in **Visual Studio 2022** (or later).  
2. (Optional) Update the watch directory and settings in `App.config`.  
3. Build the solution (`Ctrl + Shift + B`).  
4. Run the application (`F5`).  
5. Place test files in the monitored directory and watch the magic happen!

